Package org.universAAL.ui.dm.adapters

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AdapterDialogPrivacyLevel
    Adapter that takes new PrivacyLevel and applies it to the UIRequest.
    AdapterMessageInternationalization  
    AdapterUIPreferences
    Adapter that takes data from user UIPreferencesSubProfile (stored in CHE and exposed by Profile server).
    AdapterUserImpairments
    Adapter that takes user Impairments (stored in CHE and exposed by Profile server).
    AdapterUserLocation
    Acts as context subscriber to location of a given User and adds this location info to all UIRequests for that user.
